# Update version

1. Fetch
2. Check for new stable tags
3. Checkout latest new tag
4. Ensure/update node-sass to latest version in 4.14 series: https://www.npmjs.com/package/node-sass?activeTab=versions
5. Update audit results: npm audit fix --only=prod
6. Force update audit resutls: npm audit fix --only=prod --force

# Build instructions:

1*. If this wasn't done already, run: npm install
2. Run ./build-firefox
3. Install generated zip to firefox: dist/dist-firefox-<version>.zip

